    "description": "This CT angiography or CT enterography structured report template was created by members of the Society of Abdominal Radiology GI Bleeding Disease-Focused Panel. Instructions for using this template are included throughout the document. The purpose of this template is to provide a framework for reporting CT angiography or CT enterography in patients with GI bleeding. This template should be modified to comply with individual institutional requirements. ",
